{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Lost Hope</strong> is a horror game based on the Backroooms universe, where you have to solve puzzles to progress through the story, explore mysterious places filled with strange and incomprehensible things, and the locals won't let you leave the place so easily, if there is any way out at all...  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Based On the Backrooms Universe.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  <br><i>All levels were made by hand.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600830/extras/dis2.png?t=1738094660\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embark on an exciting journey through more than 10+ different levels. In each level, a thrilling story intertwines with challenging puzzles, offering different escape routes fraught with danger at every turn.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600830/extras/lvl98_2.gif?t=1738094660\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600830/extras/fas.png?t=1738094660\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dive into the exciting story, which unfolds in an abandoned laboratory Last Hope inc., where you will play as one character to uncover the story of the other.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Will you be able to reveal all the secrets of this place?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600830/extras/maxim1.gif?t=1738094660\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600830/extras/fr.png?t=1738094660\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Face more than 5+ entities, each with its own feature and mechanics. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Knowledge of each entity will help you progress through the levels and storyline.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Will you be able to escape this place in one piece?</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600830/extras/8.jpg?t=1738094660\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Also the game features a <strong>No Entity Mode</strong> if you want to just explore levels without being hunted.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"The Lobby","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2600830/a2393f8c3922a7ce264a2cfba6320fa5433902c4.jpg"},{"name":"Escaped?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2600830/0583ba4229cb2368718884eb2e6449d5f714a445.jpg"},{"name":"Pipe Dreams","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2600830/5bbff34f69ada7b00dce92a98103206f4d2e7ce0.jpg"},{"name":"In one piece","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2600830/5c0191bae304360afda54d269dba58c247e72f31.jpg"},{"name":"Have FUN =)","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2600830/99b63118874586fccef8a83ea4af9110ec8c2b67.jpg"},{"name":"You've left us =(","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2600830/5e365a96b48c82d79c1cb1228669335158e11f7a.jpg"},{"name":"Kitty House","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2600830/90348d9fe41672fbf723bf3bbc60bd7289418fef.jpg"},{"name":"Appropriate Toy","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2600830/9e43c1f91f7a5bbf13e6a7f6bdb26d